      "date": "2013-05-08 15:35:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAndreas,  If I directly observe a umount cmd with strace in the most recent sles11sp2 update I no longer see a stat() before the amount() syscall.  However this is only true on the most recent update (kernel version 3.0.74).  I believe this problem still exists in the sles11sp2 version currently in use in our test framework.   Should really only abandon this patch after we update our in use version.",
