        "subject": "LU-2181 tests: test failure on conf-sanity, subtest 45",
        "message": "LU-2181 tests: test failure on conf-sanity, subtest 45\n\nDisable additional subtest 45 for SLES11 SP2.\nAs in previous failures seen in LU-2181 the umount command in SLES 11\nstats the mountpoint before doing the umount syscall, which leads to hangs\nwhen the MDS is unavailable.\nThis test failure was only seen in full test runs so wasn't seen and fixed\nin the previous patch.\n\nTest-Parameters: clientdistro=sles11sp2 testlist=conf-sanity envdefinitions=SLOW=yes\nSigned-off-by: Bob Glossman <bob.glossman@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I09af0e6e21c1d823077e3142688fddb71b57c8a2\n"
